data.description: Well maintained and clean home available in the Country Crossing area of Fountain, CO. First glance shows a manicured lawn perfect for gardening. Upstairs you'll find master complete with en-suite 5-piece bath along with two other bedrooms and separate full bath. Kitchen and full dining area along with breakfast nook area complete the front-door-level floor. Next, you'll find a cozy living area with gas fireplace and entertainment center along with garage access. The basement floor includes a bedroom, bathroom, laundry room, as well as utility closet. This home was owned by a master electrician who installed many upgrades throughout the home.
